<!-- ===== OUR STORY ===== -->
<section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-7" data-aos="fade-right">
                <div class="section-badge">Our Story</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">From a Small Office to a <span>Trusted Name</span></h2>
                <div class="section-line" style="margin-bottom:24px;"></div>
                <div class="story-text">
                    <p>mangalpath was founded in 2015 in Jaipur, Rajasthan, with a simple yet powerful idea — to become the one-stop solution that people could rely on for their most important financial and lifestyle decisions. What started as a small consultancy helping individuals secure personal loans has grown into a comprehensive multi-service platform.</p>
